This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3746

Statusline with comprehensive information about current vim buffer.

Depends on vim window size, watchdog will show most important information: e.g. filename, how vim detected filetype, current line/cursor position.

If there are would be enough space to show additional information, watchdog will show it. For instance, file encoding and last modification date/time.

https://github.com/avakarev/vim-watchdog
